   PENNEY-AD-COLUMN (Undated) _ After a three-month review that
began with the dismissal of Temerlin McClain in Irving, Texas, J.C.
Penney's agency for almost nine years, the retailer named DDB as
its agency of record. DDB will develop marketing initiatives for
the flagging Penney department stores and catalog as well as its
shopping Web site. By Stuart Elliott.
