his desk teaching himself how to play `Dixie' on the touch-tone
phone.'' (Actor Tommy Lee Jones on his Harvard roommate, Harvard
Crimson, April 17) &QL;   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; VICE PRESIDENT OF THE WEEK: &LR;  &QL;
