or she will agree with me by and large on almost all issues.'' (Pat
Buchanan on choosing his vice president, National Journal Hotline,
April 18) &QL;   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; REDUCED CIRCUMSTANCES: &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   The Bushes earned $1.3 million in 1999 and paid federal taxes of
$514,000. In 1998 their income was $18.4 million, and they paid
$3.8 million. &QL;
