   GLASS-COLUMN _ WASHINGTON _ H.L. Mencken once said that if you
stood the country on its edge, all the loose nuts would tumble down
into Southern California. That notion will be tested anew in August
when the Democrats gather in Los Angeles. (Andy Glass is a
columnist for Cox News Service in the Washington bureau.) MOVED
THURSDAY FOR SUNDAY.
