guy wears a white hat, and the bad guy wears black. These easily
distinguished roles carry over into the history, the stories and
the myth about law enforcement in the West. Texas Rangers say the
reality of the past is not that clear, and the reality of the
present is not that exciting. (Pierson, Waco Tribune-Herald). 38.
