<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NEW&AMP;NOTABLE-AZ </SLUG>
 R  
 
 &HT;    (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)(a) 
 &HT;    By BILL MULLER 
 &HT;    c.2000 The Arizona Republic(a) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   (Editors: RETRANSMITTING FOR THOSE WHO MAY HAVE MISSED THIS.
