   POLITICS
</P>
<P>
   POLITICS-POLITE _ WASHINGTON _ Enough, already! The purveyors of
politeness and civility have had it with the nation's unruly
political candidates and the rude lot of journalits who egg them
on. Perhaps ``politics ain't beanbag,'' but we need some politeness
in our politics, they say. ``It is the rules of etiquette that
