<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-21 19:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3792 &Cx1f; tab-z
u l BC-CNS-ONLINE-BILLS &LR;      04-21 1305
